            h3.mobile-name Jeremy Butler
            p Mobile Engineering Student
            p Jeremy Butler toured the world playing music, but returned to his first love of programming through The Iron Yard. He is now developing applications for State Farm.
            a.mobile-link(href="/stories/jeremy") Read Jeremy's story
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3
