          .student-copy
            h3.fee-name Matt Bertino
            p Front End Engineering Student
            p Matt Bertino left a great job in big finance to pursue his dream of building a company. After graduating from The Iron Yard he joined our Digital Health accelerator program.
            a.fee-link(href="/stories/matt") Read Matt's story
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3
          a(href="/stories/michelle"): img(src="/images/home/student-michelle.png")
          .student-copy
            h3.design-name Michelle Child
            p Web Design Graduate
            p After working as an English teacher abroad, Michelle became enthralled with the web design industry. She joined The Iron Yard and found a job within weeks of graduation.
            a.design-link(href="/stories/michelle") Read Michelle's story
        .col-xs-12.col-sm-6.col-lg-3  
          a(href="/stories/astrid"): img(src="/images/home/student-astrid.png")
          .student-copy
            h3.rails-name Astrid Countee
            p Rails Engineering Graduate
            p Astrid Countee was a data analyst working in oil and gas when she decided to pursue her passion for building software. She now enjoys a succssful freelance career.
            a.rails-link(href="/stories/astrid") Read Astrid's story


  .container.code-school-section 
    .row(style='margin-bottom: 120px;')
      .col-md-7.col-xs-12
        h2 Intensive Code School
        p(style="margin-bottom: 0px;") The Iron Yard Academy teaches intensive, three-month courses that mentor you into a professional junior-level programmer. Our program goes far beyond tactical skills and teaches you to think like a software engineer. Programming is a lifelong study, and our process shows you to learn how to learn so you remain highly valuable for the rest of your career.
        a.btn.discover-courses(href="/courses") Discover Our Courses
      .col-md-5.col-xs-12(style="padding-top: 45px;") 
        img(src="/images/home/students-home.jpg")
        .caption Our students come from all walks of life. Join The Iron Yard family! 

  .container-fluid.gray-light-bg.courses
    .container.courses-section
      .row
        .course-box.fee-eng
          img(src="/images/home/fee-icon.png")
          .fee-header front end engineering
          p Learn to build in-browser apps in the Front End Engineering program using HTML, CSS and JavaScript and basic server-side tech. At the end of the class you’ll have the skills to create beautiful, fully functional websites and web applications.
          a.btn(href="/courses/front-end-engineering") find out more
        .course-box.web-design
          img(src="/images/home/wd-icon.png")
          .design-header web design
          p Learn Web Design from the ground up, including ideation, UI and UX design, front-end code and a whole lot more.
          a.btn(href="/courses/web-design") find out more
        .course-box.rails-eng
          img(src="/images/home/rails-icon.png")
          .rails-header rails engineering
          p Learn Ruby on Rails, one of the most popular server-side frameworks in the world. You’ll know how to build fast, production-quality full-stack apps.
          a.btn(href="/courses/rails-engineering") find out more
        .course-box.mobile-eng
          img(src="/images/home/mobile-icon.png")
          .mobile-header Mobile Engineering
          p Learn iOS app development using Xcode 5 and a whole lot of Objective-C. At the end of the class you’ll have the skills to create beautiful, fully functional iOS apps and the foundation to pursue building Mac apps.
          a.btn(href="/courses/mobile-engineering") find out more
        .course-box.python-eng
          img(src="/images/home/python-icon.png")
          .python-header Python Engineering
          p Learn to analyze data and publish insights using Python and machine learning. At the end of the class you’ll make magic happen with real-world data sets and you'll know how to build web apps to show off your wizardry.
          a.btn(href="/courses/python-engineering") find out more
        .course-box
          h2 now accepting applications
          a.btn.apply-now(href="https://theironyard.typeform.com/to/EcL2Zc") apply now
          br
          a.about-tuition(href="/courses/tuition") Learn about tuition

